# MKError.Code.loadingThrottled

**Case**

The data didn’t load because data throttling is in effect.

## Declaration

```swift
case loadingThrottled
```

## Discussion

This error can occur if an app makes frequent requests for data over a short period of time.

## Constants

- **MKError.Code.decodingFailed**: GeoJSON decoding failed.
- **MKError.Code.directionsNotFound**: The framework couldn’t find the specified directions.
- **MKError.Code.placemarkNotFound**: The specified placemark could not be found.
- **MKError.Code.serverFailure**: The map server was unable to return the desired information.
- **MKError.Code.unknown**: An unknown error occurred.
